{"_path":"/maps/_ai/evaluation/reproducibility","_dir":"evaluation","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Reproducibility","description":"机器学习可重复性（Reproducibility）的核心价值与实践方法，包括随机种子固定、数据版本控制等关键实践。","original_path":"_ai/reproducibility.md","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"title-ml-可重复性description-机器学习可重复性reproducibility的核心价值与实践方法"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"title: ML 可重复性\ndescription: 机器学习可重复性（Reproducibility）的核心价值与实践方法"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"ml-可重复性为何重要"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ML 可重复性为何重要？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可重复性不是\"锦上添花\"，而是 ML 系统的核心支柱。没有它，调试变成无头苍蝇，模型改进沦为猜测游戏，团队协作寸步难行。在受监管行业（金融、医疗、自动驾驶），证明模型行为的一致性更是合规的必要条件。正如名言所说：\"If it isn't reproducible, it's not science.\" —— 在 MLOps 中，不可重复的模型在生产环境中不可能稳健。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"实现-ml-可重复性的六大实践"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"实现 ML 可重复性的六大实践"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"版本化一切"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：用 Git 管理代码，用 DVC（Data Version Control）管理数据和模型，建立完整的版本控制闭环"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"确保确定性"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：固定随机种子（PyTorch/TensorFlow 的 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"manual_seed"}]},{"type":"text","value":"），设置 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"cudnn.deterministic = True"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，消除随机性带来的不确定性"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"测试可重复性"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：训练完模型后用相同输入验证，确保结果一致"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"追踪实验"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：使用 MLflow 等工具记录运行 ID、超参数、环境信息，确保任何成功运行都可复现"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"数据版本追踪"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：记录数据文件版本和校验和，验证数据集一致性"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"环境容器化"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：用 Docker 捕获完整软件环境，避免\"在我机器上能跑\"的问题"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"pytorch-可重复性完整配置"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"PyTorch 可重复性完整配置"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"pre","props":{"className":"language-python shiki shiki-themes material-theme-lighter github-light github-dark monokai","code":"import random, numpy as np, torch\n\ndef set_seed(seed=42):\n    random.seed(seed)\n    np.random.seed(seed)\n    torch.manual_seed(seed)\n    torch.cuda.manual_seed_all(seed)\n    torch.backends.cudnn.deterministic = True\n    torch.backends.cudnn.benchmark = False\n","language":"python","meta":"","style":""},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"__ignoreMap":""},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"class":"line","line":1},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"style":"--shiki-light:#39ADB5;--shiki-light-font-style:italic;--shiki-default:#D73A49;--shiki-default-font-style:inherit;--shiki-dark:#F97583;--shiki-dark-font-style:inherit;--shiki-sepia:#F92672;--shiki-sepia-font-style:inherit"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"import"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"style":"--shiki-light:#90A4AE;--shiki-default:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;--shiki-sepia:#F8F8F2"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":" random"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"style":"--shiki-light:#39ADB5;--shiki-default:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#